342
00:29:11,681 --> 00:29:15,921
I invested a lot of money, energy, and time into it.

343
00:29:15,921 --> 00:29:18,100
I would give anything.

344
00:29:18,100 --> 00:29:20,081
I know you are against it,

345
00:29:20,081 --> 00:29:23,884
but if you try to understand him, you will agree with him.

346
00:29:23,884 --> 00:29:28,060
I'm sorry, I can't understand or agree.

347
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:30,280
