363
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:35,164
 Yang Bawan!

364
00:31:36,781 --> 00:31:40,600
Even in my dream, you're still so timid.

365
00:32:26,741 --> 00:32:30,061
You did this teaming with Yang Bawan, right?

366
00:32:39,100 --> 00:32:41,241
Oh, my!

367
00:32:41,241 --> 00:32:44,241
I can't hide anything from my Goddess Qin.

368
00:32:44,241 --> 00:32:47,512
However, I am not teaming with him.

369
00:32:47,512 --> 00:32:52,160
At best, I am just helping him.

370
00:32:53,180 --> 00:32:55,480
During yesterday's break…

371
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:57,044
 Yang Bawan.

372
00:32:57,701 --> 00:32:59,561
 I'll talk to you when she's gone.

373
00:32:59,561 --> 00:33:02,281
