374
00:33:02,281 --> 00:33:04,820
 You both seem strange today.

375
00:33:04,820 --> 00:33:06,541
 What happened?

376
00:33:06,541 --> 00:33:08,001
 Nothing.

377
00:33:08,001 --> 00:33:10,201
 Tell me now. I can help you.

378
00:33:10,201 --> 00:33:12,341
He kept begging me.

379
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:16,340
 Did you know Xiaoqin grows green mandrake?

380
00:33:16,340 --> 00:33:18,401
 I didn't know.

381
00:33:18,401 --> 00:33:20,221
 That thing has never sprouted.

382
00:33:20,221 --> 00:33:21,961
 Then how does she know it's green?

383
00:33:21,961 --> 00:33:23,880
 Don't interrupt me.

384
00:33:24,380 --> 00:33:28,801
 She kept saying once it sprouted, everything would be fine.

385
00:33:28,801 --> 00:33:30,300
 But then yesterday,

386
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:34,701
 I saw her pour a pot of boiling water over that flower pot.

387
00:33:35,781 --> 00:33:39,801
Unexpectedly, at nearly 22:50 before lights out,

388
00:33:39,801 --> 00:33:43,380
